title: Regrò

title: Beyond Fossil Fuels

title: Furua

title: Khalon Bridge

Established a bank account and business account on CoinBase, preparing to invest in web development and 501(c)(3) tax status.

title: Defi Biolabs
projectDescription: Bioengineering algae to reduce greenhouse gas emissions.
